00:03:28,210 --> 00:03:33,700
"Long tresses draped by her face lazily, the moon shines upon the pear blossoms.

53
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:36,850
Moaning for her loved one dearly,

54
00:03:36,850 --> 00:03:40,660
when will you be back, my love?"

55
