I can't believe Shen Jinghong actually composed such an amorous poem.

56
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:48,690
And yet people revered him as Young Master Jinghong.

57
00:03:48,690 --> 00:03:51,660
My, my. This is disgraceful.

58
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:55,150
Young Lady, but you were reading his poem with such zeal.

59
00:03:55,150 --> 00:04:01,620
Because I'm not a demure lady like others.

60
00:04:01,620 --> 00:04:05,030
You keep mentioning how much you appreciate Young Master Jinghong, too.

61
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:08,300
Well, because Young Master Jinghong
is our cash cow.

62
00:04:08,300 --> 00:04:09,760
Naturally, I admire him.

63
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:12,710
There's no way I'm mistreating my cash cow.

64
00:04:13,530 --> 00:04:17,040
Why did you bring me here to Fuyun Temple this early morning?

65
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:19,050
It's said that prayers made here will be answered.

66
00:04:19,050 --> 00:04:20,680
Today's Buddha's birthday.

67
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:25,320
All of the disciples come here to offer incense and pray for their success in the examination.

68
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:29,890
Everyone comes seeking blessings from Bodhisattva, but only limited qualification spots exist.

69
00:04:29,890 --> 00:04:31,520
Which one should Bodhisattva give her blessing to?

70
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,220
You have given Bodhisattva a hard time, you know?

71
00:04:33,220 --> 00:04:35,730
Needless to say, the most sincere believer will be blessed.

72
00:04:35,730 --> 00:04:39,971
By the way, Young Lady, you must watch your words when we pray before Bodhisattva.

73
00:04:39,971 --> 00:04:44,280
People know that fame is nothing but immaterial.

74
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,460
Still, everyone yearns for it.

75
00:04:45,460 --> 00:04:48,260
The more, the better.

76
00:04:48,260 --> 00:04:50,710
Praying for nothing at Fuyun Temple. 
  ("Nothing" and "Fuyun" are homophones.) 

77
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:52,790
What a unique turn of mind.

78
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:12,690
Young Lady, kneel at the center so that Bodhisattva can see you right away.

79
00:05:19,330 --> 00:05:23,930
Merciful Bodhisattva, please bless Young Lady with the top place in the examination.

80
00:05:23,930 --> 00:05:26,040
If not, the second place is good too.

81
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:29,540
Also, please bless her witha healthy, safe, and long life.

82
00:05:29,540 --> 00:05:32,330
May she lead a happy life.

83
00:05:32,330 --> 00:05:35,540
Isn't that too much to ask with your paltry offering?

84
00:05:35,540 --> 00:05:38,270
It's greedy, though.

85
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:43,320
Merciful Bodhisattva, I don't have much money.

86
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:48,200
But as long as you can bless Young Lady, I can do anything for you.

87
00:05:53,890 --> 00:05:57,330
Young Lady, what wish did you make to Bodhisattva?

88
00:05:58,910 --> 00:06:02,420
Everyone here seeks blessings from Bodhisattva.

89
00:06:04,030 --> 00:06:06,110
And she has to respond to each of them.

90
00:06:06,110 --> 00:06:09,690
I wish Bodhisattva to be happy every day.

91
00:06:12,330 --> 00:06:17,180
Young Lady, Madam Lu told me there will be a Fuyun Poetry Gathering at Liuyun Pavilion later.

92
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:20,760
Perhaps we'll get to witness Young Master Jinghong with his marvelous poems here.

93
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,760
So I'm bringing you there.

94
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:26,640
You can memorize all his poems and transcribe them into another collection for sale.

95
00:06:28,220 --> 00:06:30,730
Juli, I'll leave this task to you.

96
00:06:30,730 --> 00:06:32,650
My stomach hurts. I got a stomach ache.

97
00:06:32,650 --> 00:06:33,860
- You have to handle this now. 
 - Young Lady, wait.

98
00:06:33,860 --> 00:06:35,560
Young Lady!

99
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:04,960
Greetings, My Lord.

100
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:07,080
Why are you here?

101
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:10,270
Did you hint to me to come to the back mountain

102
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:14,540
when you showed the back of your head to me just now?

103
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:18,710
Did I guess wrong?

104
00:07:19,330 --> 00:07:21,640
Your explanation is unconvincing.

105
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,900
Well, then.

106
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:26,170
Because I think everywhere else is crowded, except for the back mountain.

107
00:07:26,170 --> 00:07:29,800
Maybe you wouldn't want to speak with me in a crowded place.

108
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:33,070
That's why I came here to try my luck.

109
00:07:33,070 --> 00:07:37,450
And I'm truly lucky.

110
00:07:38,090 --> 00:07:40,450
Do you even believe in luck?

111
00:07:40,450 --> 00:07:46,780
You didn't show any sign of sincerity before Bodhisattva just now.

112
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:51,930
People seek blessings from Bodhisattva, but I wish her a happy life.

113
00:07:51,930 --> 00:07:56,000
In that case, aren't I the one who treats Bodhisattva the best?

114
00:07:56,000 --> 00:08:00,120
Why didn't you seek blessings like others did?

115
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:03,560
I'd rather seek blessings from you than from Bodhisattva.

116
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,080
The examiner is right in front of me.

117
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:08,300
I mustn't waste the chance that's nearest to me.

118
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:33,500
- Please, Wen. 
 - Thank you.

119
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:50,570
My Lord.

120
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:55,900
Why did you want to see me?

121
00:08:55,900 --> 00:09:00,260
Where did you learn about the Revival Powder?

122
00:09:00,260 --> 00:09:04,330
My mother told me when I was little.

123
00:09:04,330 --> 00:09:08,980
However, she only knew a few ingredients like the Immortal Fruit.

124
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:11,790
She had no ideaabout the complete prescription.

125
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:16,270
I've sent men to ask all famous physicians in the capital about it,

126
00:09:16,270 --> 00:09:19,530
but no one has heard about the Revival Powder.

127
00:09:19,530 --> 00:09:21,850
Not even the Imperial Academy of Medicine?

128
00:09:21,850 --> 00:09:26,990
Why are you so sure that it's from the Imperial Academy of Medicine?

129
00:09:28,710 --> 00:09:31,470
Ingredients of the Revival Powder are precious,

130
00:09:31,470 --> 00:09:34,850
especially the Immortal Fruit, which is outrageously hefty.

131
00:09:34,850 --> 00:09:38,660
I couldn't think of anyone else except for the Imperial Academy of Medicine to afford such precious herbs.

132
00:09:38,660 --> 00:09:44,340
Besides, I haven't heard about this prescription from the commoners.

133
00:09:44,340 --> 00:09:48,600
I've already looked into the Imperial Academy of Medicine, but nothing has been found.

134
00:09:49,830 --> 00:09:54,330
Did your mother make a mistake on this?

135
00:09:54,330 --> 00:09:56,630
My Lord, let me tell you this.

136
00:09:56,630 --> 00:10:01,230
My mother didn't remember much about her childhood times.

137
00:10:01,230 --> 00:10:06,550
However, she had deep impressions on particular memories she had, especially the Immortal Fruit.

138
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:10,230
Oh, right.

139
00:10:10,230 --> 00:10:12,130
The Immortal Fruit.

140
00:10:12,830 --> 00:10:16,351
My Lord, you should look into its origin and consumption

141
00:10:16,351 --> 00:10:19,000
if you found nothing about the prescription.

142
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,350
Immortal Fruit is a precious ingredient.

143
00:10:20,350 --> 00:10:24,750
I suppose only the royal families of various nations have them.

144
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:26,760
In that case,

145
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:31,880
how did you identify the smell on Yun Xiangyue's garment as the Immortal Fruit?

146
00:10:34,410 --> 00:10:36,510
Well...

147
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:43,160
My father heard that the Immortal Fruit could help...

148
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:45,700
It could help to boost a man's vigor.

149
00:10:45,700 --> 00:10:50,800
So he spent a fortune to obtain one before and recruited a famous physician to study it.

150
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:55,480
I've seen it before in my family's medical room.

151
00:10:56,960 --> 00:11:01,760
It seems that you got to witness all kinds of exotic treasures

152
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:05,160
because of the affluent Mu family in Jiangnan.

153
00:11:07,230 --> 00:11:09,030
You flatter me.

154
00:11:09,030 --> 00:11:10,230
My Lord,

155
00:11:10,230 --> 00:11:14,710
you might find some clues by looking into the origin and consumption

156
00:11:14,710 --> 00:11:17,460
of the Immortal Fruit.

157
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:19,500
This is a useful lead.

158
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:21,730
I will look into it.

159
00:11:21,730 --> 00:11:23,510
However...

160
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:28,500
You are still suspicious.

161
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:39,590
 It's bound to happen, anyway. 

162
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:49,500
 Bravo! 

163
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:13,820
 The affair of Jishan Hall has been keeping me busy lately. 

164
00:12:13,820 --> 00:12:17,270
 I will come if I have time. 

165
00:12:17,270 --> 00:12:19,460
 Well played. 

166
00:12:25,930 --> 00:12:27,660
 It's been some time since I played this. 

167
00:12:27,660 --> 00:12:29,160
 Brother Shen. 

168
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:34,120
 Is Brother Shen going to make a performance, too? 

169
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,740
 Maybe. 

170
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:47,940
I don't know much about the guqin.

171
00:13:49,110 --> 00:13:56,010
However, the melody gave me a sense of carefreeness and boundlessness.

172
00:13:57,500 --> 00:14:00,280
- Greetings, Your Highness. 
  - Greetings, Your Highness. 

173
00:14:01,630 --> 00:14:05,410
You flatter me, Your Highness.

174
00:14:06,710 --> 00:14:09,880
No need to feel constrained.

175
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:12,730
Please continue. Be relaxed.

176
00:14:12,730 --> 00:14:16,180
I came here to learn something, too.

177
00:14:18,970 --> 00:14:23,080
My Lord, if the Revival Powder is a unique prescription,

178
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:27,170
why would I dig my own grave by revealing it to you?

179
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:32,720
Only you and your mother know about this.

180
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:37,730
By any chance, did your mother create this?

181
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:41,040
My Lord,

182
00:14:41,040 --> 00:14:44,260
it seems that you've run a thorough background check on me.

183
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:48,170
I came from the Mu family in Jiangnan.

184
00:14:48,170 --> 00:14:54,170
My mother was sold into a house of ill repute because of the family's downfall in her early years.

185
00:14:54,170 --> 00:14:57,770
She couldn't remember her parents' names,

186
00:14:57,770 --> 00:15:01,390
so she gave herself a name.

187
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:06,550
Afterward, my father gave her a new name, Gu Yixiao.

188
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:10,560
 Mother, I read a poem today. 

189
00:15:10,560 --> 00:15:13,980
 "Reminiscing my earlier time when I departed. When I departed, the willow was drifting along with the breeze." 

190
00:15:16,530 --> 00:15:19,920
 Mother, can you tell me where you are from? 

191
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:23,760
 Like the fallen petals from an unknown tree... 

192
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:28,170
 outside the window, I don't know where I came from. 

193
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:46,090
The metropolitan examination isn't your only goal to come to the capital. Right?

194
00:15:48,160 --> 00:15:51,690
You seem to know everything.

195
00:15:51,690 --> 00:15:54,850
Why bother asking me?

196
00:15:54,850 --> 00:15:58,600
That's your personal affair. I won't pry.

197
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:05,110
But you should know what I want.

198
00:16:05,110 --> 00:16:10,900
My Lord, I know about Revival Powder because of my mother.

199
00:16:12,450 --> 00:16:16,050
But as for how she came to know about it,

200
00:16:16,050 --> 00:16:20,110
I'm finding it bizarre too.

201
00:16:20,110 --> 00:16:23,830
Since I was little, she taught me how to read and write.

202
00:16:23,830 --> 00:16:28,540
She taught me medical skills and life principles.

203
00:16:28,540 --> 00:16:32,250
However, I'm clueless

204
00:16:32,250 --> 00:16:35,840
about how she knew so much knowledge.

205
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:42,640
As of now, she's buried six feet underground.

206
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:47,860
Where she came from remains mysterious to me.

207
00:16:48,990 --> 00:16:54,660
I'd be grateful to you if you can find the answer for me.

208
00:16:58,320 --> 00:17:00,640
I already know.

209
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:05,580
My Lord, do I have your trust now?

210
00:17:05,580 --> 00:17:07,540
No.

211
00:17:10,260 --> 00:17:11,970
But I trust...

212
00:17:14,740 --> 00:17:18,260
the sincere love of the children for their parents.

213
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:27,370
So, do you believe me or not?

214
00:17:28,470 --> 00:17:32,560
"Like a homeless wayfarer,

215
00:17:32,560 --> 00:17:36,840
I have nowhere to make port.

216
00:17:36,840 --> 00:17:40,360
Eager to earn myself a great name,

217
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:44,820
yet times have failed me."

218
00:17:44,820 --> 00:17:47,890
 Well done! 

219
00:17:47,890 --> 00:17:51,480
This poem is good and artistic.

220
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:58,260
However, a hesitant man wouldn't achieve something big.

221
00:17:58,260 --> 00:17:59,800
Your Highness...

222
00:18:00,630 --> 00:18:02,550
Come.

223
00:18:05,060 --> 00:18:08,380
I heard that you're renowned for your poetry talent in the capital, Young Master Jinghong.

224
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:14,210
Why don't you grace us with your new poems today?

225
00:18:14,210 --> 00:18:17,740
Brother Shizong, I believe the First Prince came here

226
00:18:17,740 --> 00:18:21,430
to help Shen Jinghong garner more attention.

227
00:18:21,430 --> 00:18:23,790
No need to be mad. Here.

228
00:18:23,790 --> 00:18:27,670
I guess he's going to secure his place on the top rank this year.

229
00:18:34,740 --> 00:18:39,200
"My aspirations never once swayed despite meritorious achievements."

230
00:18:42,410 --> 00:18:46,840
"Thousand years of history have been left in oblivion.

231
00:18:46,840 --> 00:18:50,780
I shall stand down as the nation nestles in peace.

232
00:18:50,780 --> 00:18:55,690
Triumphing above all names of this era."

233
00:18:55,690 --> 00:18:59,780
 What a marvelous one! 

234
00:19:03,840 --> 00:19:07,300
"Upon withered grass and frosty sand,

235
00:19:07,300 --> 00:19:10,610
warriors are rapturous in bloodshed.

236
00:19:10,610 --> 00:19:14,010
Yet Yin Mountain is shielded from the clamor of war,

237
00:19:14,010 --> 00:19:17,550
surrounded by clover meadows with a serene moon on high."

238
00:19:17,550 --> 00:19:21,310
 Well said! Nice poem! 

239
00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:24,450
"Drunk in a dream, losing direction,

240
00:19:24,450 --> 00:19:27,380
sunset is cut short as Chinese francolins cry.

241
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:31,540
Gentle spring showers fall onto the river,

242
00:19:33,260 --> 00:19:36,890
I bid farewell to my friends as red maple leaves pile up high."

243
00:19:36,890 --> 00:19:39,260
 Great poem! 

244
00:19:39,260 --> 00:19:41,060
 Excellent! 

245
00:19:41,060 --> 00:19:43,540
"Low clouds urge the sun to set...

246
00:19:44,220 --> 00:19:46,820
and strong gusts curl the flags up.

