00:19:48,060 --> 00:19:50,780
- Wailing of swan geese at boundary halt, 
 - It's Young Master Jinghong.

248
00:19:50,780 --> 00:19:54,180
I savor tea in the southern garden peacefully.

249
00:19:54,180 --> 00:19:55,970
A calm plume of smoke around the amber sky,

250
00:19:55,970 --> 00:19:58,920
- garrison stays guard at the frontier. 
 - Come with me.

251
00:19:58,920 --> 00:20:01,260
And the expanse of the horizon

252
00:20:01,260 --> 00:20:04,790
- appears serene and harmonious. 
 - Come on.

253
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:09,530
The lonely cloud astonishes the moon from afar.

254
00:20:09,530 --> 00:20:12,550
The old heroes now have grizzled hair."

255
00:20:12,550 --> 00:20:16,310
His Lordship still wants to meet Miss Mu, which means they're still helpful to us.

256
00:20:16,310 --> 00:20:17,540
Go with her and see what she wants to say.

257
00:20:17,540 --> 00:20:21,960
- "Never has he forgotten the great vow, 
 - Go.

258
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:26,700
- Shall not return until peace is secured." 
 - Are you good at making mental notes?

259
00:20:26,700 --> 00:20:30,310
Do you remember everything Young Master Jinghong said just now?

260
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:34,230
Can you transcribe them for me?

261
00:20:34,230 --> 00:20:36,230
I need them.

262
00:20:37,290 --> 00:20:40,490
But my handwriting is ugly.

263
00:20:40,490 --> 00:20:43,230
It's fine, as long as you can record everything.

264
00:20:43,230 --> 00:20:45,980
Please. Please help me.

265
00:20:47,170 --> 00:20:48,680
 One more, Brother Shen. 

266
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:51,990
 That's right. One more, Shen. 

267
00:20:51,990 --> 00:20:55,010
"Three thousand iron-armored knights,

268
00:20:55,010 --> 00:20:57,380
a million war-flagged armies,

269
00:20:58,370 --> 00:21:04,210
and sturdy soldiers are ready to depart as the drum sounds.

270
00:21:06,650 --> 00:21:09,710
An imposing valiance held within

271
00:21:09,710 --> 00:21:12,450
and boasted with brilliant strategies.

272
00:21:17,020 --> 00:21:19,550
Righteous loyalists stand tall...

273
00:21:21,270 --> 00:21:24,500
even though they are not young anymore."

274
00:21:24,500 --> 00:21:29,780
"Gunpowder rampages cities and walls collapse.

275
00:21:31,090 --> 00:21:36,480
Embers reflect on war-hardened armor, lonely in the dead of night."

276
00:21:37,810 --> 00:21:42,960
"White bones repose underneath the sand along the homeward road.

277
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:48,210
The sound of the war bell and temple drum heralds news of victory."

278
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:55,900
Did I write anything wrong?

279
00:21:55,900 --> 00:21:57,360
No.

280
00:21:57,360 --> 00:21:59,080
Did I miss out on something?

281
00:21:59,080 --> 00:22:00,520
No.

282
00:22:01,360 --> 00:22:05,260
But it hurts my eyes to read your handwriting.

283
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:09,710
   

284
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:24,160
I'm impressed by your "Righteous loyalists stand tall even though they are not young anymore."

285
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:26,720
I have indeed chosen the right person.

286
00:22:27,560 --> 00:22:30,560
It was a reckless and poor performance, Your Highness.

287
00:22:30,560 --> 00:22:36,600
I prefer recklessness over those feeble and pretentious complaints.

288
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:41,020
Composing poetry is just a trivial skill for entertainment.

289
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:44,140
You're right.

290
00:22:44,140 --> 00:22:48,880
I can tell you're ambitious and patriotic.

291
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:51,820
You must be the pillar of the nation in the future.

292
00:22:52,840 --> 00:22:54,120
The metropolitan examination is around the corner.

293
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:56,320
I shall look forward to your performance.

294
00:22:58,840 --> 00:23:00,560
Much obliged, Your Highness.

295
00:23:23,280 --> 00:23:26,060
I didn't expect the First Prince to be here.

296
00:23:26,060 --> 00:23:30,440
I heard that His Highness is interested in poetry, especially borderland poems.

297
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:32,040
Besides, he likes martial arts and is intrepid.

298
00:23:32,040 --> 00:23:35,020
That's why he's close to you.

299
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:42,960
Everyone knows that you treat the three princes equally.

300
00:23:44,360 --> 00:23:49,380
My Lord, but Shen Jinghong has had a flawed reputation recently.

301
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:53,380
Why did you bring him up all of a sudden?

302
00:23:53,380 --> 00:23:56,640
Shen Jinghong does make a name for himself in the capital,

303
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:59,160
but he has made the scholars mortified.

304
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:01,520
He isn't well-regarded in the circle.

305
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:04,200
If His Highness intends to help him develop his potential,

306
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:07,980
it's best if he can help him restore his reputation first.

307
00:24:08,840 --> 00:24:10,440
How?

308
00:24:11,000 --> 00:24:16,180
Even though Shen Jinghong's literary talent is known to the entire capital,

309
00:24:16,180 --> 00:24:20,040
he lacks a good lofty reputation.

310
00:24:20,040 --> 00:24:24,740
Not only that, many of his poems only circulated among theaters.

311
00:24:24,760 --> 00:24:29,640
But given his ambitious poems about the borderland today,

312
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:34,160
he managed to ignite passion and a sense of admiration in those listeners.

313
00:24:36,320 --> 00:24:40,100
What do all these have to do with me?

314
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,700
My Lord,

315
00:24:42,700 --> 00:24:46,660
His Highness cares about his man.

316
00:24:46,660 --> 00:24:52,040
Could you please be nice to me, too?

317
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:01,380
Who sent you here?

318
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:06,360
Well, I am always on your side, My Lord.

319
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:13,060
What do you want me to do?

320
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:16,560
My Lord,

321
00:25:16,560 --> 00:25:21,500
there's been a price hike in the capital recently, especially for writing supplies.

322
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:26,120
Though I come from the Mu family, I'm just an undesirable daughter of a concubine.

323
00:25:26,120 --> 00:25:28,080
I didn't bring much money...

324
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:31,480
when I came to the capital.

325
00:25:33,600 --> 00:25:40,980
Well, I've been helping you a little these days. Right?

326
00:25:41,740 --> 00:25:46,980
Truth be told, even ladies in Xiaoqin Pleasure House paid me two sycees for my treatment.

327
00:25:46,980 --> 00:25:48,500
That day...

328
00:25:53,520 --> 00:25:58,280
During the literary gathering in Wenzheng Parlor, I sat beside your table.

329
00:25:58,800 --> 00:26:03,260
Do you remember what you said?

330
00:26:05,040 --> 00:26:09,740
Did you hear everything?

331
00:26:09,740 --> 00:26:11,140
I did.

332
00:26:14,040 --> 00:26:18,980
I know I've spoken my heart out about my admiration for you.

333
00:26:18,980 --> 00:26:22,380
Why do you ask since you already heard it?

334
00:26:22,380 --> 00:26:25,280
I feel shy.

335
00:26:26,620 --> 00:26:29,840
Did you really speak your heart out?

336
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:31,040
Certainly.

337
00:26:31,040 --> 00:26:34,340
My admiration and loyalty to you are genuine.

338
00:26:34,340 --> 00:26:37,120
The whole world can bear witness to it.

339
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:41,780
Do you admire me because I'm reckless and I took undeserved credit?

340
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:49,020
Well...

341
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:54,540
I thought you were planning to lure the enemy with yourself.

342
00:26:54,540 --> 00:26:58,280
As the old saying goes, the distinguished ones shouldn't expose themselves in a vulnerable place.

343
00:26:58,280 --> 00:27:01,660
I was worried about you.

344
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,660
Thank you, My Lord!

345
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:22,960
This is great!

346
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:25,180
Zhimo, you're so kind.

347
00:27:26,960 --> 00:27:28,200
Zhimo!

348
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:29,700
Why...

349
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:33,740
I'm sorry.

350
00:27:33,740 --> 00:27:36,100
I lost control of myself.

351
00:27:36,100 --> 00:27:38,020
Does it hurt?

352
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:42,460
I didn't mean to sprain your arm.

353
00:27:42,460 --> 00:27:45,640
I must send you to see a physician now.

354
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:56,280
Did you reattach your arm?

355
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:03,660
Zhimo, how brilliant of you!

356
00:28:06,560 --> 00:28:08,060
My Lord.

357
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:14,200
Weirdly, Mu Zhuohua shows up here at this time.

358
00:28:14,840 --> 00:28:18,740
Besides, she knows the secret about the Revival Powder.

359
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:21,800
She's suspicious.

360
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:26,580
This matter concerns the lives of 30,000 soldiers.

361
00:28:27,380 --> 00:28:30,420
We need to test her again.

362
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:31,860
Understood.

363
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:35,880
Tonight, go and fetch Mu Zhuohua.

364
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:39,300
We're taking her to Tiantong Mountain.

365
00:28:39,840 --> 00:28:43,120
Are you suspecting that she has something to do with the mastermind behind it?

366
00:28:43,120 --> 00:28:46,440
I'd like to find out if this person...

367
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:52,500
matches my suspicions.

368
00:28:53,280 --> 00:28:56,440
I see, you're luring her into the trap to kill two birds with one stone.

369
00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:58,160
This is wise, My Lord.

370
00:28:58,870 --> 00:29:01,670
   

371
00:29:19,680 --> 00:29:21,920
Greetings, Your Highness.

372
00:29:24,080 --> 00:29:27,620
I heard that you composed great poems at the Fuyun Poetry Gathering.

373
00:29:27,620 --> 00:29:29,980
Your poetic talent has greatly pleased my brother.

374
00:29:29,980 --> 00:29:33,320
It's a pity that you weren't there, Your Highness.

375
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:38,280
I was occupied with the affairs of Jishan Hall, and I couldn't make it this morning.

376
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:41,800
You must be tired, Your Highness.

377
00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:48,680
Chen'er has a discerning eye for talents.

378
00:29:48,680 --> 00:29:52,480
It's not a bad thing being noticed by him.

379
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:55,280
I should congratulate you.

380
00:29:55,280 --> 00:30:00,340
After today's Fuyun Poetry Gathering, you'll likely make a name for yourself.

381
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:04,000
It's because of your advice, Your Highness.

382
00:30:05,000 --> 00:30:06,920
Young Master Shen, you're a man of great talent.

383
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:10,140
I have plenty of collections in my study.

384
00:30:10,140 --> 00:30:13,680
You can read them if you want.

385
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:17,780
Hopefully, you can triumph in the examination and represent scholars from humble roots.

386
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:20,100
I appreciate that, Your Highness.

387
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:24,220
But concerning the current situation,

388
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:29,220
the tide of humble scholars can't be turned by my effort alone.

389
00:30:30,080 --> 00:30:32,540
But surely that's all the more reason you should stand up first.

390
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:37,580
Someone has to take the first step to inspire others to follow in their footsteps.

391
00:30:39,600 --> 00:30:41,500
I agree with you.

392
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,600
Your Highness,

393
00:30:48,600 --> 00:30:51,600
were you playing the Immortal Seeking game?

394
00:30:52,280 --> 00:30:54,320
Do you know this?

395
00:30:55,040 --> 00:30:57,660
Not much.

396
00:30:58,240 --> 00:31:01,360
Would you like to have a round with me?

397
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:06,920
I will, as long as you wish.

398
00:31:08,480 --> 00:31:10,120
   

399
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:12,760
Be honest with me. Why did Lord Ding give you so much money?

400
00:31:12,760 --> 00:31:14,040
Did you curry favor with him?

401
00:31:14,040 --> 00:31:15,560
I don't have the guts.

402
00:31:15,560 --> 00:31:19,060
I just tricked him a little.

403
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:25,580
You see, Lord Ding is a dangerous character who doesn't trust others easily.

404
00:31:25,580 --> 00:31:30,900
But the problem is, we have to meet him because of the Revival Powder.

405
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:33,340
Tell me. What more can I do, then?

406
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,960
You must gain his trust.

407
00:31:38,760 --> 00:31:41,640
I realized that although he's known as a nefarious demon,

408
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:45,060
not only is he not bloodthirsty, but also a little bit easy to talk with.

409
00:31:45,060 --> 00:31:48,880
So, I employed a bit of my wit today.

410
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:52,000
You managed to earn 500 taels today.

411
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:55,280
It's not merely wit. It's wisdom.

412
00:31:55,760 --> 00:31:58,680
Dealing with a dangerous and strong opponent,

413
00:31:58,680 --> 00:32:03,500
not only should I show my strengths but also some weaknesses.

414
00:32:03,500 --> 00:32:07,900
A capable but greedy subordinate is more manageable.

415
00:32:09,960 --> 00:32:12,540
If so, does Lord Ding trust you now?

416
00:32:12,540 --> 00:32:14,080
How is that possible?

417
00:32:14,080 --> 00:32:19,860
People who have experienced death on the battlefield like him won't place trust in others easily.

418
00:32:22,080 --> 00:32:28,280
Therefore, doing business with him is the best way to deal with him.

419
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:34,100
However, the Revival Powder really bugs me a lot.

420
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:36,800
You assist him and he pays you money.

421
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:38,840
Why are you troubled?

422
00:32:38,840 --> 00:32:42,640
I guess he's investigating three leads now.

423
00:32:42,640 --> 00:32:46,440
First, the record of the Immortal Fruit.

424
00:32:46,440 --> 00:32:49,160
Second, my mother's origin.

425
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:52,960
Third, the body of Deputy General Yuan.

426
00:32:54,520 --> 00:32:55,840
Juli, you know what?

427
00:32:55,840 --> 00:33:01,400
My mother told me that my grandfather used to serve at the Imperial Academy of Medicine.

428
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:06,380
The record of the Revival Powder, which even Lord Ding couldn't trace,

429
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:10,860
appeared in the medical book left by my grandfather.

430
00:33:13,760 --> 00:33:18,020
Could it be that this Revival Powder was created by him?

431
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:19,680
That's quite possible.

432
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:21,240
Perhaps this is a secret prescription.

433
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:22,560
Oh no, this is bad.

434
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:27,420
What if Lord Ding gets revenge on me once he discovers this?

435
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:29,080
This can't be.

436
00:33:29,080 --> 00:33:30,880
Get revenge on you?

437
00:33:31,840 --> 00:33:36,120
What should you do? Why must he blame you for past grievances?

438
00:33:37,840 --> 00:33:39,400
You said Lord Ding has a coital difficulty.

439
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:41,660
You can treat his problem, so he can...

440
00:33:41,660 --> 00:33:43,480
You must bite your tongue.

441
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:48,140
Last time, Lord Ding was sitting beside us at Wenzheng Parlor.

442
00:33:48,900 --> 00:33:52,100
- Well... Can't we even talk here? 
 - No

443
00:33:52,121 --> 00:33:54,560
We must watch our words even when we're at home.

444
00:33:54,560 --> 00:33:58,260
Who knows if someone's eavesdropping on us now?

445
00:34:00,480 --> 00:34:02,460
There is really someone outside.

446
00:34:02,460 --> 00:34:04,660
Young Lady, don't be afraid.

447
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:06,460
- I'll check it out. 
 - Go now.

448
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:13,360
We... We didn't badmouth Lord Ding!

449
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:15,540
Take the broom away.

450
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:17,800
Are you going to kill us with your sword again?

451
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:21,580
Even if I do so, the broom won't help much.

452
00:34:23,080 --> 00:34:24,780
True, though.

453
00:34:24,780 --> 00:34:26,440
What do you come here for?

454
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:28,200
You want my Young Lady to treat His Lordship again?

455
00:34:28,200 --> 00:34:29,080
Why?

456
00:34:29,080 --> 00:34:30,960
Does Lord Ding not deserve this?

457
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:33,080
Of course, Lord Ding deserves it.

458
00:34:33,080 --> 00:34:34,360
Of course, he does.

459
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:37,100
Juli, stay at home. I'll go with him.

460
00:34:37,100 --> 00:34:39,260
No. I must tag along.

461
00:34:39,260 --> 00:34:40,840
The horse is ready.

462
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:42,080
Do I have to ride a horse?

463
00:34:42,080 --> 00:34:43,680
You can't ride a horse, so stay.

464
00:34:43,680 --> 00:34:45,700
I can hold onto you.

465
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,900
The latest poetry collection by Shen Jinghong will be printed soon.

466
00:34:48,900 --> 00:34:51,500
Someone from the printing house will send them over at any time.

467
00:34:51,500 --> 00:34:52,520
You can't leave at this moment.

468
00:34:52,520 --> 00:34:55,840
It'll be bad if Young Master Shen loses his popularity and his poetry collection becomes unmarketable.

469
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:58,820
Will Young Master Jinghong lose his popularity in such a short time?

470
00:34:58,820 --> 00:35:03,220
After I top the examination, he'll lose his popularity by then.

471
00:35:03,220 --> 00:35:04,420
You're right, Young Lady.

472
00:35:04,420 --> 00:35:05,620
You must be careful.

473
00:35:05,620 --> 00:35:07,380
Come home early. The examination is approaching.

474
00:35:07,380 --> 00:35:09,080
Take care of our home.

475
00:35:11,560 --> 00:35:12,980
Coming.

476
00:35:12,980 --> 00:35:14,160
You must be very careful, Young Lady.

477
00:35:14,160 --> 00:35:15,180
Take care of our house.

478
00:35:15,180 --> 00:35:16,680
Let's go.

479
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:28,360
Slow down!

480
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:37,620
My Lord, here she is.

481
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:42,360
I didn't tell you to bring her here in this way.

482
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:44,461
Isn't she great? I bet she can ride a horse.

483
00:35:44,461 --> 00:35:45,560
Just drop the act.

484
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:47,680
I can't ride a horse.

485
00:35:47,680 --> 00:35:49,380
I really can't.

486
00:35:51,640 --> 00:35:53,540
Forget it.

487
00:35:53,540 --> 00:35:56,480
Pass your medicine chest to Zhimo. You'll ride with me.

488
00:35:57,720 --> 00:35:59,220
What?

489
00:35:59,220 --> 00:36:00,640
Pass me the medicine chest.

490
00:36:00,640 --> 00:36:02,140
All right.

491
00:36:10,160 --> 00:36:11,660
Come on.

492
00:36:14,560 --> 00:36:17,260
What... What?

493
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:20,340
Come on.

494
00:36:20,340 --> 00:36:25,880
I... My Lord. My legs... My legs are numb.

495
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:28,080
I'm having a cramp.

496
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:42,200
My Lord.

497
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:45,400
Where are we going?

498
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:50,140
I need you to check on a dead body.

499
00:36:50,160 --> 00:36:52,100
I'll double the reward.

500
00:36:53,080 --> 00:36:56,040
My Lord, must I really go there?

501
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:58,040
The metropolitan examination is around the corner.

502
00:36:58,040 --> 00:37:01,200
I planned to study at home these days.

503
00:37:01,200 --> 00:37:04,520
Besides, I'm not a coroner.

504
00:37:04,520 --> 00:37:09,300
Well, this is beyond my knowledge...

505
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:17,900
Because I think there is something on the body that ordinary coroners can't identify.

